修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7fca39a1b6589ae7022e01520122f275d83e0faa","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58aab4099a2aa9e99b49422c57737b61a0b18ae1","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56601b240e3e56a281afc6da47e2caadeaaa2eaa","tid":1395014,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"不要說&quot;推&quot;，試著說 <br />\n#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"4edfdb43588d24228609b67e4b62b5bc20240cb0","tid":1395014,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"我哋喺香港人 我哋會罷工"},{"pid":"c36b9e5e4fb759c390ba0424eb2f2be2a5b6d3c8","tid":1395014,"uid":173444,"like":0,"