ime":"2019-08-01T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d044df520368f06dc8b9741fdac4a238c2531ab","tid":1395014,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"仲有730葵芳舉槍？"},{"pid":"7deae3defd713b63de100371d56287b3d0b41191","tid":1395014,"uid":250447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人<br />\n#我會參與罷工"},{"pid":"8a662a449fa5a4c68969ea0515e7361275fe0641","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b3b07daaf76cc50f3f5c0fb396677efe8bd59b2","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ea1c7f7b97ce33c7e9d642547a85d60b251e164","tid":1395014,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"6968bd45236e032ab13d3399b935e956b987c265","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"047f0bad80089bc5f0db23d950d7822d9ca1ef28","tid":1395014,"uid":281763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"......我覺得group一齊罷好重<br />\n但睇返&hellip;諗諗點解發起人唔發8月9罷呢。。。。呼應6月9麻(唔建議分散人，純膠突然奇想"},{"pid":"99a63098bd03f4b2db453cefde81ba529b4a6a91","tid":1395014,"uid":9974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"屯元天搞緊大西北不合作運動，110萬人無得坐西鐵就大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n北區大埔沙田手足唔好係大圍/九龍塘火車站唔小心跌野，3區人口120萬，無得坐火車出黎就大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[遍地開花］8月5朝早7點15元朗西鐵站要屯元天人！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391481\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391481</a>"},{"pid":"d193832c33dd69eb390179b800cdb140ced56b3e","tid":1395014,"uid":147888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a3c9bf2ba5ea982ceeab9efca979440f7d8d74","tid":1395014,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>感謝各位手足<br />\n有幸同大家生於同一個時代<br />\n見證著香港既興衰<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月5日一齊三罷<br />\n讓我地一齊寫下香港的歷史</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d13aeb3576453c3cb0eb6bb59c90fbb433d4282b","tid":1395014,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"731加返葵涌西灣河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b271107d59c515b0251caf50c8c88e897c36e12","tid":1395014,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚反應非常熱烈，今晚繼續"},{"pid":"047321c11c2159f72ac56362fa2c919a6fd9efa0","tid":1395014,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"eab9e936248c423b897bc9862afcf0302d109a5a","tid":1395014,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"置頂"},{"pid":"10fb5388db3758363eff9c43ba25c96ae22afe64","tid":1395014,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"163cbab2bda96c7458f244d052b278881565b65a","tid":1395014,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"8.5 我要罷工"},{"pid":"a67b8c736421ec1e541c865e8f538707c989de0b","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1e434b7bf4e46335a40a0841cc9d628ffb11594","tid":1395014,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9405f1ed51e5d2234c516958075c0d06b1451ac8","tid":1395014,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d58ec9ab9dca8fa19c49e93c9d47378d3c4d5234","tid":1395014,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"推上去 推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0780893979bfdec516541d0b4d0ab8e4626b9436","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c462943a4c5a8c32496c20210fd347793c6e4bf0","tid":1395014,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:02:28.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"d6fc911e754790422d2e185ed84511923cc1e82f","tid":1395014,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"558759d56fbd9a55bd6a36ed4e550eda1e04d4cf","tid":1395014,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87e97ad9e3d000822d0c135aa6342d66d7006e","tid":1395014,"uid":264588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"967c2ca4a610fb9b323439559498d89507a96483","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79000504272c0a04ef43ee8e42c3da9c90695ce4","tid":1395014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f608665e05e9f39193c4150107207ea5986